in conjunction with something that pairs delimiters like `autopair-mode'.
"
  :type 'string
  :group 'auto-indent)

(defcustom auto-indent-eol-char ";"
  "* Character inserted when
`auto-indent-key-for-end-of-line-inser-char-then-newline' is
